---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { amazonUrl, images } from '../utils/site';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section
    class="relative bg-cover bg-center text-center py-[50px]"
    style={`background-image: url('${images.heroBackground}')`}
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/50 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[1140px] px-4">
      <h1 class="mb-4 font-bebas text-[60px] font-semibold leading-none tracking-[1.4px] text-primary md:mb-12 md:text-[126px] lg:text-[163px]">
        NOW AVAILABLE!
      </h1>
      <a href={amazonUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Order now at Amazon" class="my-4 inline-block md:my-6">
        <img
          src={images.amazonButton}
          alt="Order now at Amazon"
          width="300"
          height="111"
          class="mx-auto inline-block max-w-[55%] transition-transform hover:scale-105 motion-reduce:hover:scale-100 md:max-w-[350px]"
        />
      </a>
      <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-4 md:mt-8 md:gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <h2 class="self-center text-center font-abril text-[30px] font-black leading-[1.4] text-primary lg:-mt-24 md:text-[clamp(30px,4vw,50px)] md:leading-[1.2]">
          Hey everyone, my new book is published!
        </h2>
        <div>
          <img src={images.bookMockup} alt="Clowning from the Heart book cover" width="768" height="1045" fetchpriority="high" class="mx-auto w-full rounded" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Book Section -->
  <section class="bg-white p-[25px] md:px-[50px] md:pt-[50px] md:pb-[25px]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1140px]">
      <h2 class="mb-8 text-center font-bebas text-[35px] font-semibold uppercase leading-none tracking-[1.4px] text-primary md:text-[clamp(35px,4vw,50px)]">
        One smile at a time changed thousands of lives starting with one unexpected calling
      </h2>
      <div>
        <p class="mb-4 text-left leading-normal text-body">
          <i><b>Clowning from the Heart</b></i> is the true story of Cindy Love's unexpected calling to become "Sparkle," a gospel clown who brought joy, hope, and God's love into hospitals, schools, parades, and places marked by pain.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-left leading-normal text-body">
          Through tender encounters with wounded children, skeptics, and strangers carrying heavy burdens, Cindy discovered a simple truth: healing often begins with being seen, heard, and loved. What started as a step of obedience became a ministry rooted in compassion, faith, and the quiet power of presence.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 mb-4 text-left leading-normal text-body">
          This heartfelt memoir shares how God uses ordinary people and simple acts of kindness to reach broken hearts and spark something miraculous.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Author Section -->
  <section class="bg-white px-[25px] pt-0 pb-[25px] md:px-[50px] md:pt-[25px] md:pb-[50px]">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-[1140px] grid-cols-1 items-center gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <img src={images.headshot} alt="Cindy Love-Sprengel" width="640" height="610" loading="lazy" class="block w-full" />
      </div>
      <div class="self-center">
        <p class="mb-3 text-body">
          Cindy Love-Sprengel was born and raised in California City, a small town in the Mojave Desert. As an adult, she became a self-taught clown, discovering along the way that authenticity and joy are what truly bring a clown to life.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-3 text-body">
          For 35 years, Cindy served as "Sparkle the Clown," using humor, compassion, and faith to bring comfort and connection to people of all ages. Through her work, she learned that joy can open doors where words cannot, and that even the smallest act of kindness can leave a lasting impact.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-3 text-body">
          Cindy is a devoted mother of two and grandmother of four, whom she lovingly calls the light of her world. She now lives in Walla Walla, Washington with her husband, Lew. When she's not clowning, Cindy enjoys knitting, crocheting, and crafting. She also shares her home with three cats, two Shih Tzus, and one Yorkshire Terrier.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-3 text-body">
          Through <i><b>Clowning from the Heart</b></i>, Cindy invites readers into her story of obedience, compassion, and the quiet power of bringing joy where it's needed most.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Review Section -->
  <section
    class="relative overflow-hidden bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat pt-12 pb-12"
    style={`background-image: url('${images.reviewBackground}')`}
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/[.28] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[1140px] px-[25px] text-center md:px-[50px]">
      <h2 class="mb-2 font-bebas text-[35px] font-semibold tracking-[1.4px] text-white md:text-[clamp(35px,4vw,50px)]">
        NOW AVAILABLE!
      </h2>
      <a href={amazonUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Order now at Amazon">
        <img
          src={images.amazonButton}
          alt="Order now at Amazon"
          width="300"
          height="111"
          loading="lazy"
          class="mx-auto inline-block max-w-[300px] transition-transform hover:scale-105 motion-reduce:hover:scale-100"
        />
      </a>
      <h3 class="mt-1 mb-0 font-bebas text-[35px] font-semibold uppercase leading-none tracking-[1.4px] text-white md:text-[clamp(35px,4vw,50px)]">
        Help me share my book to the world
      </h3>
      <div class="text-left text-white">
        <p class="mb-3"><i>Dear Friend,</i></p>
        <p class="mb-3">
          <i>Thank you for reading Clowning from the Heart! My hope is that Sparkle's journey has encouraged you, made you smile, and inspired you to see the ways God can use even the smallest acts of love to make a difference.</i>
        </p>
        <p class="mb-3">
          <i>One of the most powerful ways to help others discover this story is by leaving a review on Amazon (and Goodreads, etc.). Your honest words can show how laughter, compassion, and obedience can touch lives and inspire hearts.</i>
        </p>
        <p class="mb-3"><i><b>Why Reviews Matter</b></i></p>
        <p class="mb-3">
          <i>Your review helps readers see that ministry, faith, and hope can come in unexpected forms, one smile at a time. Even a few sentences can encourage someone to open this book and be transformed.</i>
        </p>
        <p class="mb-3"><i><b>How to Leave a Review</b></i></p>
        <ol class="mb-3 list-decimal pl-12">
          <li class="mb-1"><i>Go to the <a href={amazonUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-green-link no-underline hover:text-green-link/80"><b>Clowning from the Heart</b></a> Amazon page</i></li>
          <li class="mb-1"><i>Scroll to <b>Customer Reviews</b></i></li>
          <li class="mb-1"><i>Click <b>"Write a customer review"</b></i></li>
          <li class="mb-1"><i>Share your thoughts, what part of Sparkle's story touched you most?</i></li>
          <li class="mb-1"><i>Give a star rating and click <b>Submit</b></i></li>
        </ol>
        <p class="mb-3"><i><b>Starter Ideas</b></i></p>
        <p class="mb-3"><i>"This book reminded me that God can use anyone, anywhere, to bring light and joy."</i></p>
        <p class="mb-3"><i>"Cindy Love's story of Sparkle inspired me to look for ways to serve with compassion and love."</i></p>
        <p class="mb-3"><i>"From laughter to heartfelt moments, every page shows the power of presence, kindness, and faith."</i></p>
        <p class="mb-3"><i><b>Thank You!</b></i></p>
        <p class="mb-3">
          <i>Every review helps others discover the joy, hope, and love in this story. Your voice matters and can be part of spreading God's light — one smile at a time.</i>
        </p>
        <p class="mb-3"><i>With gratitude,</i></p>
        <p class="mb-0"><i><b>Cindy Love</b></i></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-primary py-4 px-6 text-center text-sm text-white">
    <p class="m-0">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Sparkle. All rights reserved. Powered by <a href="https://spiritmedia.us" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white/80">Spirit Media</a>.</p>
  </footer>
</Layout>
